{
  "title": "nc",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">nc是netcat的简写，有着网络界的瑞士军刀美誉。因为它短小精悍、功能实用，被设计为一个简单、可靠的网络工具.</span><br>"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "data": "[官方说明](http://www.tutorialspoint.com/unix_commands/nc.htm)"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><h1 data-evernote-id=\"136\" class=\"js-evernote-checked\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding-top: 5px; font-size: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18pt;\">nc的控制参数不少，常用的几个参数如下所列：</span></h1></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">1) -l</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;\">用于指定nc将处于侦听模式。指定该参数，则意味着nc被当作server，侦听并接受连接，而非向其它地址发起连接。</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">2) -p &lt;port&gt;</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;\">暂未用到（老版本的nc可能需要在端口号前加-p参数，下面测试环境是centos6.6，nc版本是nc-1.84，未用到-p参数）</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">3) -s</span>&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;\">指定发送数据的源IP地址，适用于多网卡机&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">4) -u</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;指定nc使用UDP协议，默认为TCP</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">5) -v</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;\">输出交互或出错信息，新手调试时尤为有用</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">6）-w</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;\">超时秒数，后面跟数字&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">7）-z</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;\">表示zero，表示扫描时不发送任何数据</span></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<pre class=\"prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;lucida console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-image: url(file:///images/codecolorer_bg.gif); background-color: rgb(251, 251, 251); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-position: center top; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span class=\"pln\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">nc </span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);\">[-</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">hlnruz</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);\">][-</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">g</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);\">&lt;网关...&gt;][-</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">G</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);\">&lt;指向器数目&gt;][-</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">i</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);\">&lt;延迟秒数&gt;][-</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">o</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);\">&lt;输出文件&gt;][-</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">p</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);\">&lt;通信端口&gt;][-</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">s</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);\">&lt;来源位址&gt;][-</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">v</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);\">...][-</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">w</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);\">&lt;超时秒数&gt;][主机名称][通信端口...]</span></pre>"
    },
    {
